 \\sim 10^4$ yr. Our\nobservations demonstrate that the measured physical properties of 66P are\nconsistent with other typical short-period comets and differ significantly from\nother MBCs. Therefore, 66P is unlikely to have a main belt origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Sep 2019 18:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
