ant p}(G)$ (resp. all $\\mu \\in \\mathcal{M}_{1,\\leqslant\np}(G)$) of the probability that $\\mathbf{G}_{\\mu}$ is connected. We determine\n$f_{1,G}(p)$ and $F_{1,G}(p)$ exactly when $G$ is a path, a complete graph and\na cycle of length at most $5$.\n  Many new problems arise from our work, which are discussed in the final\nsection of the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Sep 2019 15:12:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 08:26:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-29"}
