e the work function and electric field strength are\nmuch higher) the contribution of the relativistic correction about 10 % has\nbeen established.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Sep 2019 11:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
